<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The guarantor must have his normal residence or an establishment in the Community and, subject to the provisions of the Treaty concerning freedom to supply services, must be approved by the competent authority of the Member State in which the security is given. </inglise>
<eesti> Garandi alaline elu- v&otilde;i asukoht peab olema &uuml;henduses ning garandil peab olema arvestades asutamislepingu teenuste osutamise vabadust k&auml;sitlevaid s&auml;tteid selle liikmesriigi p&auml;deva asutuse heakskiit, kus tagatis antakse. </eesti>
<inglise> The guarantor shall be bound by a written guarantee. </inglise>
