<inglise> Article 19 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 19 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The security shall be released when: </inglise>
<eesti> Tagatisest vabastatakse, kui: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) final entitlement to the sum granted as advance has been established, or </inglise>
<eesti> a) ettemaksena makstud l&otilde;ppsumma n&otilde;ue on kindlaks tehtud, v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise> (b) the sum granted, plus any addition provided for in the specific Regulation, has been repaid. </inglise>
<eesti> b) ettemaksusumma ning erim&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud t&auml;iendavad summad on tagasi makstud. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Once the deadline for showing final entitlement to the sum granted has passed without production of evidence of entitlement, the competent authority shall immediately follow the procedure in Article 29. </inglise>
<eesti> Ettemaksena makstud l&otilde;ppsumma n&otilde;ude&otilde;iguse t&otilde;estamiseks m&auml;&auml;ratud t&auml;htaja &uuml;letamisel, ilma et oleks esitatud n&otilde;uet kinnitavaid t&otilde;endeid, kohaldab p&auml;dev asutus viivitamata artiklis 29 s&auml;testatud korda. </eesti>
<inglise> However, where Community legislation so provides, evidence may still be produced after that date against partial repayment of the security. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui &uuml;henduse &otilde;igusaktid seda ette n&auml;hakse, v&otilde;ib t&otilde;endusmaterjali esitada siiski ka p&auml;rast k&otilde;nealust kuup&auml;eva tagatise osalise tagasimaksu vastu. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> If the force majeure provisions in Community legislation permits repayment of the advance alone, the following further conditions shall apply: </inglise>
<eesti> Kui v&auml;&auml;ramatut j&otilde;udu k&auml;sitlevates &uuml;henduse &otilde;igusaktides s&auml;testatakse ainult ettemaksu tagasimaksmise v&otilde;imalus, kohaldatakse j&auml;rgmisi lisatingimusi: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) the circumstances claimed as force majeure shall be notified to the competent authority not later than 30 days after the day on which information was received by the party concerned that circumstances indicating a possible case of force majeure had arisen, and </inglise>
<eesti> a) v&auml;&auml;ramatu j&otilde;una esinevatest asjaoludest teatatakse p&auml;devale asutusele hiljemalt 30 p&auml;eva jooksul alates p&auml;evast, mil asjaomane osapool sai teada asjaoludest, mille alusel v&otilde;ib t&otilde;deda, et tegemist on v&auml;&auml;ramatu j&otilde;uga, ja </eesti>
<inglise> (b) the party concerned shall repay the sum advanced or the relevant part of it within 30 days from the date on which the competent authority issues a request for repayment. </inglise>
<eesti> b) asjaomane osapool maksab ettemakstud summa v&otilde;i selle asjakohase osa tagasi 30 p&auml;eva jooksul alates p&auml;deva asutuse poolt v&auml;ljastatud tagasimaksen&otilde;ude kuup&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise> If the conditions laid down at (a) and (b) are not respected, the terms of repayment shall be the same as if circumstances of force majeure had not occured. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui punktides a ja b s&auml;testatud tingimusi ei t&auml;ideta, kehtivad samad tagasimaksetingimused, kui v&auml;&auml;ramatut j&otilde;udu ei oleks esinenud. </eesti>
